@books

= Книги

(источники, выделенные жирным шрифтом, активно использовались при написании)

**Berman, Sheri. The Social Democratic Moment. Harvard University Press, 1998.**

Childers, Thomas. The Nazi Voter : The Social Foundations of Fascism in Germany, 1919-1933. Chapel Hill : University of North Carolina Press, 1983. Internet Archive, http://archive.org/details/nazivotersocialf0000chil.

Deak, Istvan. Weimar Germany’s Left-Wing Intellectuals: A Political History of the Weltbühne and Its Circle. 1st ed. University of California Press, 1968. https://doi.org/10.2307/jj.13167943.

**Dobkowski, Michael N., and Isidor Wallimann. Towards the Holocaust: The Social and Economic Collapse of the Weimar Republic. 1983. https://surface.syr.edu/books/17/.**

Fowkes, Ben. The German Left and the Weimar Republic: A Selection of Documents. Brill, 2014. https://brill.com/display/title/20472.

Гуттсман, В. Л. Социал-демократическая партия Германии, 1875-1933: от гетто к правительству. Routledge, 2019.

**Harsch, Donna. German Social Democracy and the Rise of Nazism. University of North Carolina Press, 1993.**

Kolb, Eberhard. The Weimar Republic. Unwin Hyman, 1988.

McMeekin, Sean. The Red Millionaire: A Political Biography of Willy Münzenberg, Moscow’s Secret Propaganda Tsar in the West. Yale University Press, 2003. https://www.jstor.org/stable/j.ctt1npbws.

Miller, Frederick Alfred. Left-Wing Splinter Parties in the Weimar Republic. University of British Columbia, 1974.

Mommsen, Hans. The Rise and Fall of Weimar Democracy. UNC Press Books, 2017.

Orlow, Dietrich. Weimar Prussia, 1925–1933: The Illusion of Strength. University of Pittsburgh Pre, 1991.

Rosenberg, Arthur. A History of the German Republic. 1936, https://www.marxists.org/archive/rosenberg/history-weimar/index.htm.

Rosenhaft, Eve. Beating the Fascists?: The German Communists and Political Violence 1929-1933. Cambridge University Press, 1983.

Sender, Toni. The Autobiography of a German Rebel, 1940. http://archive.org/details/TheAutobiographyOfAGermanRebel.

Shirer, William L. The Rise and Fall of the Third Reich: A History of Nazi Germany. Simon & Schuster, 2011.

**Smaldone, William. Confronting Hitler: German Social Democrats in Defense of the Weimar Republic, 1929-1933. Lexington Books, 2010.**

Woytinsky, Wladimir. Stormy Passage. Vanguard Press, 1961. Internet Archive, http://archive.org/details/Woytinsky-Stormy-passage.


